question: What is the description of the type of the company who concluded its contracts most recently?
gold: SELECT T1.company_name FROM Third_Party_Companies AS T1 JOIN Maintenance_Contracts AS T2 ON T1.company_id  =  T2.maintenance_contract_company_id JOIN Ref_Company_Types AS T3 ON T1.company_type_code  =  T3.company_type_code ORDER BY T2.contract_end_date DESC LIMIT 1

question: Find the list of documents that are both in the most three popular type and have the most three popular structure.
gold: SELECT document_name FROM documents GROUP BY document_type_code ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 3 INTERSECT SELECT document_name FROM documents GROUP BY document_structure_code ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 3

question: What are the names of documents that have both one of the three most common types and one of three most common structures?
gold: SELECT document_name FROM documents GROUP BY document_type_code ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 3 INTERSECT SELECT document_name FROM documents GROUP BY document_structure_code ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 3
